{"id":152526,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/湖北襄樊一军人对老人施暴，1500名群众抗暴，掀翻/","date":"2011-05-16T02:00:39Z","modified":"2011-05-16T02:00:39Z","title":"湖北襄樊一军人对老人施暴，1500名群众抗暴，掀翻军车","content":"<p><div><span>    茉莉花革命发起者博客收到湖北省襄樊市茉莉花支持者们发来的图文。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">       2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日晚，湖北省襄樊市一名军人，在行驶到人民路与华丰路附近时，认为一位过路的老人挡住了他的去路，并大肆辱骂该老人。军人随即下车，拔出手枪就对着老人说：“给老子让路，不然就开枪打死你！”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>    老人不屈服，勇敢反抗，周围的群众岂能容忍这样的事情，上来制止军人胡作非为。随后</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>赶到现场，军人拿出证件扔给警察，自己悠然的坐在车里面刮胡子，随后点燃一支烟，悠闲自得。此时的场景引起周围群众极大的愤怒，随后暴乱开始，群众最多时达到1500</span><span>人以上。当时警察为控制局势，不得不把军人的枪没收了，并令军人待在车中。该警察被打伤了，众人当场连军人在内把军车掀翻，大量防爆警察随即赶到，看到个个武装到牙缝的警察，愤怒的群众没有被吓到。警民冲突升级，愤怒的群众掀翻了从人民路到前进路口的护栏，冲突持续到当晚午夜时人群才逐渐散去。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>                      </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nK-IyPSbOEM/Tc9VF2njo5I/AAAAAAAAAbc/ydCf7NHTbCY/s1600/0d7f57b696b39d7d63d09f92.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nK-IyPSbOEM/Tc9VF2njo5I/AAAAAAAAAbc/ydCf7NHTbCY/s320/0d7f57b696b39d7d63d09f92.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qpdhUjr7COg/Tc9VGyhowsI/AAAAAAAAAbg/Vw7aFnI1Q6k/s1600/8c68c4dd5fcbcb70c75cc389.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qpdhUjr7COg/Tc9VGyhowsI/AAAAAAAAAbg/Vw7aFnI1Q6k/s320/8c68c4dd5fcbcb70c75cc389.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ILASrCu2u9g/Tc9VHqFShAI/AAAAAAAAAbk/KbCzplMN5fU/s1600/19f5b94ad26c36a6c2ce79d6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ILASrCu2u9g/Tc9VHqFShAI/AAAAAAAAAbk/KbCzplMN5fU/s320/19f5b94ad26c36a6c2ce79d6.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-c68K13z2-P4/Tc9VIq4qSVI/AAAAAAAAAbs/6q6LdpNcPzg/s1600/0110600b752af17e43a75b8c.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-c68K13z2-P4/Tc9VIq4qSVI/AAAAAAAAAbs/6q6LdpNcPzg/s320/0110600b752af17e43a75b8c.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KBIngGeUA40/Tc9VJx8-HFI/AAAAAAAAAbw/HdjcC0QnYPs/s1600/a9fafd157a6e096caec3ab96.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KBIngGeUA40/Tc9VJx8-HFI/AAAAAAAAAbw/HdjcC0QnYPs/s320/a9fafd157a6e096caec3ab96.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PnUhfBAr9kU/Tc9VK8bAbSI/AAAAAAAAAb0/J2rZOPETrnE/s1600/a5737f91cd7248a750664f6d.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PnUhfBAr9kU/Tc9VK8bAbSI/AAAAAAAAAb0/J2rZOPETrnE/s320/a5737f91cd7248a750664f6d.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-HpRODOT4dWQ/Tc9VMLoMwhI/AAAAAAAAAb4/cS_CBn61-Ks/s1600/f7ef5a980d652c410ff477c8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-HpRODOT4dWQ/Tc9VMLoMwhI/AAAAAAAAAb4/cS_CBn61-Ks/s320/f7ef5a980d652c410ff477c8.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-EkI1nfteUCQ/Tc9VEnml0hI/AAAAAAAAAbY/jl4-eM1Bsno/s1600/0a76f52115eb84ae08d18718.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-EkI1nfteUCQ/Tc9VEnml0hI/AAAAAAAAAbY/jl4-eM1Bsno/s320/0a76f52115eb84ae08d18718.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DItioHjNPK0/Tc9VHyRgOiI/AAAAAAAAAbo/Vl57LgdiiNo/s1600/614ba185d85234494b540318.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-DItioHjNPK0/Tc9VHyRgOiI/AAAAAAAAAbo/Vl57LgdiiNo/s320/614ba185d85234494b540318.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<p>[中国茉莉花革命发起者 http://molihuaxingdong.blogspot.com] 转载请注明出处</p>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googl